   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">This feature enables you to add one or more participants in the program.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">To add a participant, please follow the below steps:</p>
      <ol class="- topic/ol ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">Go to the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Participants</b> page.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Add Participant.</b>
            <fig class="- topic/fig ">
               <image placement="break"
                      width="700"
                      href="../attachments/102432701/107118614.jpg"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </fig>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Enter or select the participants' name which you want to add, in the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Account Name</b> column. Please view the below image.<fig class="- topic/fig ">
               <image placement="break"
                      width="700"
                      href="../attachments/102432701/107118613.jpg"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </fig>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Save.</b>
            <p class="- topic/p ">The participant is added.</p>
            <note type="note" class="- topic/note ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">
                  <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Note</b>
               </p>
               <p class="- topic/p ">The system will throw a validation if the same participant is added multiple times in an overlapping time period.</p>
            </note>
         </li>
      </ol>
